  | Niche           | Trend Score | Search Growth | Publishing Growth | Insight                         |
  |-----------------|-------------|---------------|-------------------|---------------------------------|
  | Racing Romance  | 46.6        | +908%         | +18%              | Huge demand, supply catching up |
  | Cowboy Romance  | 29.6        | +560%         | -78%              | Massive unmet demand            |
  | Grumpy Sunshine | 27.9        | +78%          | +1260%            | Supply flooding market          |
  | F1 Romance      | 14.1        | +163%         | +75%              | Growing niche, balanced         |
  | Hockey Romance  | 11.1        | +136%         | -45%              | High demand, undersupplied      |

  Key Opportunities:
  - Cowboy romance: 560% search growth but -78% publishing = readers want it, publishers aren't delivering
  - Hockey romance: 136% search growth but -45% publishing = similar gap
  - Racing/F1: Explosive search growth, publishing is responding

● Key insights from the time series:

  Sports Romance 1 - Hockey exploded in late 2025, hitting peak 100. Baseball and racing growing from small bases.

  Sports Romance 2 - "Sports romance" as a category spiked massively. Basketball/soccer emerging.

  Historical - Historical romance spiking hard recently. Viking/Scottish growing from near zero = untapped.

  Emerging - "Spicy romance" shows sustained upward trajectory since 2023. Monster romance steady growth.

  Paranormal - Dragon romance had a viral moment (late 2024 spike), fae romance quietly growing.

